Basic problem on strings:
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Problems_on_strings

Classical:
String Search

Single string:
Longest alternating subsequence (Longest zig-zag subsequence)
Longest increasing subsequence
Longest palindromic substring
Longest repeated substring problem
Lexicographically minimal string rotation

Two strings:
v Longest common substring problem
v Longest common subsequence problem
Shortest common supersequence problem
v String-to-string correction problem (shortest edit distance)

Special:
Separating words problem

DS:
Suffix Tree
suffix array
Trie

Test:
http://javarevisited.blogspot.co.uk/2015/01/top-20-string-coding-interview-question-programming-interview.html


Alternatives:
find shortest substring, such that the concatenation of one or more copies of it results in the original string
